	&lt;li&gt;Make the variable non-static;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Change the fork mode in the maven configuration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I prefer the second option, but I was wondering if folks have an opinion.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
